    def assert_not_user_site():
        # create a finalized easy_install command
        dist = Distribution()
        dist.script_name = 'setup.py'
        cmd = ei.easy_install(dist)
        cmd.args = ['py']
        cmd.ensure_finalized()
        assert not cmd.user, 'user should not be implied'
